headline: Want Decades of Passive Income? 3 Stocks to Buy Now and Hold Forever
summary: AbbVie is a Dividend King with solid growth prospects.  Enbridge is a leading pipeline operator and natural gas utility with an ultra-high dividend yield.  Realty Income pays monthly dividends that are highly reliable.
